Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there wasn't any Hicks\Nat the time of Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.28,0:34:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nshe's confusing the name
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.33,0:34:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the name\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.45,0:34:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that's only nominalization\NI can't control what people ask me you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.82,0:34:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,well I'm not going to ask you anything\Nmy weather
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.82,0:34:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,stormy weather field\Nlikes to be in your weather field
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.47,0:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nyou bet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern the level of truth of a statement\Nyou know you calibrate the level of truth you see
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.98,0:34:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need a personal opinion\Nyou just calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.25,0:34:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the level of that\Nand what's the level of this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.25,0:35:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they may come out of different contexts\Nhello Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.31,0:35:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing is true in this context\Nand the other thing is true in this context
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.31,0:35:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is not true in this context\Nyou understand
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\Nhello Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.31,0:35:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you answer all my questions through your work\Nand I'm very grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.31,0:35:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thank you very much\Nhowever there is somebody very dear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.31,0:35:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants to ask you\Na question
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.31,0:35:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants what\Nwho wants to ask a question
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.31,0:35:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody wants to ask you a question\Nwhich is my dear wife
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.31,0:35:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,oh oh\Nwhere is she
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.31,0:35:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,she's at home\Noh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.31,0:35:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and she keeps asking me\Nhow come a man
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.31,0:35:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is meditating 3-4 hours a day\Nand he's always with his tapes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.31,0:35:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with his headphones on his ears\Na real man wouldn't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.31,0:35:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only answer I can tell her\Nis that it's an attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.31,0:35:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nit just happens
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.31,0:35:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she says\Nwell day by day you're getting crazier and crazier
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.70,0:36:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you're getting as that old crazy guy on TV\Nthat you're watching at
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.32,0:36:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said God willing\Nso you turn me on to this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can you please turn her off\Nyou have a divergence of alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.20,0:36:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and many relationships end because of it\None gets God struck
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.67,0:36:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other doesn't\Nand very often the one who doesn't is jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.90,0:36:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and hates the one who's God struck\Nbecause they're not God struck
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.90,0:36:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and so they do end in divorce yes\Nyou have to choose between God and her
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.24,0:36:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's her decision isn't it\Nshe's the one making the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.93,0:37:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\Nshe's the one that's turning away from God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.34,0:37:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and you turn towards God\Nyes that can cause quite a divergence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.66,0:37:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so now I can go home in peace\Nyou can go home and be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.56,0:37:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in peace\Nin peace I said
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.56,0:37:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,oh peace yeah yeah\Nyou answered the question thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.13,0:37:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you pray for her\Nokay
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.13,0:37:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,well I committed that I will serve her as I would serve God\Nso let's see what that brings
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah okay\Nthank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.13,0:37:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you doctor\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.82,0:37:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just pray secretly\Ndon't let her know you're praying
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.82,0:37:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're eating your toast in the morning\Nand look at you you flip the page
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.82,0:37:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and see you're surreptitiously praying\Nhow you doing doc
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.82,0:37:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,could you talk further about\Nthe identification with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.82,0:38:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of consciousness\Nabout what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.02,0:38:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the light of consciousness\Ncould you talk a little bit about that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.78,0:38:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's by letting go what you are not\Nthat it's revealed to you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.86,0:38:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which is the source of consciousness\Nand that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.27,0:38:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are simultaneous\Nit isn't affirming what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.68,0:38:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's probably just a thought\Ninstead you just constantly surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are not\Nand where does awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.27,0:38:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,does awareness come out of consciousness\Nthe light is consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.88,0:38:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and awareness is like a quality of consciousness\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.88,0:38:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so the light of consciousness\Nwhich is universe
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.04,0:38:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is universal\Nout of the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.55,0:39:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when it strikes matter arises life\Nsee
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.42,0:39:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is the source of life\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.42,0:39:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes protoplasmic life\Nwhen it encounters organic material
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.42,0:39:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,organic\Nnot inorganic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.64,0:39:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but organic\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.47,0:39:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so you let go of what you are not\Nit's not necessary to affirm what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.86,0:39:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,because what you are becomes\Nit's like surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.89,0:39:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it just kind of reveals itself\Nit reveals itself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.89,0:39:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and if one were to live in that silent space\Nall the time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.27,0:39:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen to the ego and the experiencer\Nthey disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.46,0:39:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.07,0:39:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hello Dr. Hawkins\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.07,0:40:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is\Nfor someone who is looking to move eventually into the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.07,0:40:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually transcend the 400s\Nwould you recommend higher education or college
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.07,0:40:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or is that necessary\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.10,0:40:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think education helps\Nit just sharpens certain faculties
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.25,0:40:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,however it's not necessary\Nit's not necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.08,0:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,anything that lifts your level of consciousness\Neducation, dedication, selfless service
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.80,0:40:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,any one of them will do it\Nthe Jesus prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.86,0:40:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to merely say the Jesus prayer from within all the time\Nyou don't need to go to college to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.37,0:40:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,see\Nso
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.50,0:40:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it depends on what\Nhow you picture your future life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.50,0:40:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's devoted to teaching\Nthen the education would be beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.04,0:41:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if instead you tend to become\Nmore a spiritual initiate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.97,0:41:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's not necessary\Nyou know some orders are
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.30,0:41:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,educative orders\Nand then there are orders that are not educative
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.34,0:41:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they are more of service\Nso you serve God by gardening
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.17,0:41:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you also serve God by translating\Ndoing the book of Kells
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.20,0:41:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,did you ever look up the book of Kells\NK-E-L-L-S
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.12,0:41:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know\Nso you see the monks
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.54,0:41:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,spent lifetimes\Ndoing this incredible work
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.02,0:41:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so\Nanything might inspire you to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.08,0:41:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,want to move in that direction\Nyou know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.40,0:41:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow I feel compelled to tell you to look up the book of Kells\NI don't know why
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.43,0:41:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nmaybe you're one of those monks reincarnated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.56,0:42:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the bathroom all the time\Ninstead of working on this
