Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.32,0:42:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,oh kitty books\Noh kitty books
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.51,0:42:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,don't show me kitty books right in the middle of the\Noh
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.69,0:42:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,stop\Nit's like incredibly beautiful music
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.34,0:42:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it just stops you in my tracks\Nif I hear a beautiful strand of music coming out of somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.60,0:42:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just done\Nuh huh
