Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.43,0:43:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo\NLord most high
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a commitment you just made\Nthank you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.89,0:43:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a wonderful one\Nyeah kitties knock me out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.74,0:43:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,puppies knock me out\Nbeautiful music knocks me out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.74,0:43:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,hello\Noh
