Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.97,0:43:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness level of mankind is shifting\Nlast month
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.97,0:43:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,right as we talk\Nyeah
