Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.68,0:45:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so what which would be the more accurate then\Nwell you want to know currently
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.68,0:45:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,currently what's its effective energy\Nso how do we rely on what a book calibrates at then at any time
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.79,0:45:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,who said I rely on it\NI'll just tell you what it calibrated at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.79,0:45:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,under those conditions\Na different person under different conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.98,0:45:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,may get a different thing because\Nthey're living on a different scale
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.98,0:45:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,than I am\Ndoes that make sense
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.94,0:45:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not\Nit's still
