Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.97,0:45:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world changes about it\Nand changes what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.97,0:45:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually changes what it is\Nand that intention also changes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.12,0:45:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is\Nso the contextualization of intention
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.15,0:45:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say if I tell you a statement\Nin the context
