Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.32,0:48:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what we do is we go at it like a brand new research\Nprogram
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.32,0:48:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to ask lots of questions\Nand a lot of times only after you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.48,0:48:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a few questions\Ndoes the reason clear up
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.48,0:48:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wouldn't go just by appearance\NI'd say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.48,0:48:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know why there's this disparity\Nand then I would start asking questions about it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.22,0:48:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,until I clarified the answer\Nlike I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.22,0:48:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you know\Nearth-warming was due to human
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.44,0:48:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,endeavor myself\Nsee
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.44,0:48:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then when I got to know I thought\Nwow
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.44,0:48:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what do I mean to know\Nalright so I would say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.70,0:48:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you know if it puzzles you\Nit would be a project
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.70,0:48:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe there's some meaning that you need to know in it\Nand that's why it comes to your attention
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.70,0:48:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea\NI would make a study of it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.70,0:49:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\Nthere must be some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.70,0:49:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you were doing the om\Ninstead of asking what does om calibrate at
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.70,0:49:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or saying om calibrates at\Nyou were going om
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.70,0:49:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at\Nso that you know I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.70,0:49:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe that's it\Nyou know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.70,0:49:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\Nanyway
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.76,0:49:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I would take any seeming disparity\Nand just ask a lot of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.76,0:49:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,until you're satisfied with the answers that you're getting\Nbecause there is an
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.76,0:49:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you know there is an explanation\Nand
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.76,0:49:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we hit puzzlers ourselves too\Nyou know we hit puzzlers
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.76,0:49:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nwe hit puzzlers
