Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.10,0:49:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to research it out\Nbut it's good to research it out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.10,0:49:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's probably some\Nthing you need to know revealed in it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.10,0:49:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why you're focusing on it\Nokay
