Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.14,0:49:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you may be bringing up something we all need to know\Nwho knows
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.58,0:49:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so thank you for looking at it\Nand bringing it up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.58,0:49:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks\NI know we get stuck with it ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.90,0:50:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we get puzzled with it\Nalso at different times
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.37,0:50:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the same thing or person will calibrate differently\Nhello Dr. Hawkins thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.33,0:50:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\NI've been in the 12 step program for the last four years
