Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.33,0:50:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a lot of progress personally in my life\Nand right now as we speak
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.33,0:50:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making some major personal changes\Nthank you
