Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.42,0:51:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,okay what's 11\N11 is sought through prayer and meditation to continue your conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.42,0:51:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue your contact with God as you understood him\Npraying only for his knowledge and his will to carry that out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.42,0:52:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,okay only for knowledge of his will for me\Nso then that comes as a knowingness and a certainty
