Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.42,0:52:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,yes\Nhi Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.83,0:52:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,yes\Nmy name is Neha
