Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.89,0:54:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,why rush it\Nso um till then my uh responsibilities should be just to focus on um
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.96,0:55:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,well you're talking about self-discipline to say you know it helps to set aside a certain time period\Nyou know I used to meditate an hour in the morning and an hour in the evening you know
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.15,0:55:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for many years see\Nalways no matter how busy life was
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.21,0:55:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,see\Nand if I had to be at the hospital early at seven o'clock I got up at five so I could meditate for an hour before I left for the hospital
