Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.60,0:55:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah it's not complicated\Noh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.63,0:56:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so my husband is going to ask another question now after me\NI wanted your blessings on us as a couple to remain aligned with the spiritual intention
