Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.57,0:56:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my goodness\Nthank you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.78,0:56:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nshe is so cute
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.78,0:56:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have a question for you\Nyes
