Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.76,1:00:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you leave\Nwhat's the problem
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.76,1:00:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to hire a video crew you know\Nand make a big drama out of it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.07,1:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very simple to die\Nyou let go wanting to live
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.52,1:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and you let go wanting to live\Nthe desire to live slips away
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.19,1:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the breathing slows down and down\Nand you can be very very close to death
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.06,1:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and still come back\Nbecause at the last moment you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.14,1:01:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still up to you\Nand then you get the karmic implications
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.14,1:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the meaning of this\Nand you then may change your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.14,1:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it is you know\Non one hand
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.48,1:01:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason we calibrate low\Nis because it's like negating divine mercy
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.06,1:01:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you see\Nas you're turning your life to God
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.05,1:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you're turning it over to the divine mercy\Nin the death process
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.05,1:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is then bearable\Ncan even be ecstatic
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.21,1:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,out of God's grace is given the strength\Nto bear death
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.28,1:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so constantly surrendered to God's grace in the matter\Nis what summons it forth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.91,1:02:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to calibrate suicide because\Npeople will go into a negative space of all of it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.75,1:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes it can be an act of bravery and courage\Nother times it can be courage
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.24,1:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be cowardice\Nso you don't know which is which
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.24,1:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't generalize it\Nit depends on who's doing it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.24,1:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or what motive\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.16,1:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hello\Nthere's a way of committing suicide which is passive
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.28,1:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you don't\Nyou just don't resist death
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.28,1:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\Nand then death takes over
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.53,1:02:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\NI have experienced chronic fatigue
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.53,1:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for over six years\Nwhat
