Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.68,1:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,intuitive knowingness\Noh yes
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.68,1:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a relationship\Nwell no I'm talking
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.68,1:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,about the perfection\Nwhere discernment
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.68,1:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes automatic\Nas a consequence
