Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.68,1:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,long before that\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.68,1:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,discerning right\Nfrom wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.68,1:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a lot\Nof discernment
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.68,1:11:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes on\Nbefore that
