Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.89,1:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you just see\Nthe wolf
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.89,1:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,bless Vicki\Nbless you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.84,1:12:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nthank you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.54,1:12:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's out\Nto get you
