Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.54,1:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna lose your\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.54,1:12:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always afraid\NI'm gonna lose it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.12,1:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or not find it\Nor forget it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.54,1:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or something\Nso we'll put it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.04,1:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where it's safe\Nhi doc
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.27,1:12:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,yes\Nno question
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.47,1:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nalright
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.57,1:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,good for you sir\Ngood for you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.40,1:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,hello\Nthis is along
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.86,1:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the same topic\Nof vegetarianism
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.10,1:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that you addressed\Njust a few questions ago
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.56,1:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,do we incur\Nour karmic debt
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.86,1:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from eating\Ndead animals
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.58,1:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if we have a respect\Nof all living things
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.10,1:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,specifically\NSpecifically, does meat-eating calibrate lower than vegetarianism?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.20,1:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegetarianism calibrates 210.\NNow, it doesn't have any spiritual positive or negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.06,1:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have only to the degree that you're fulfilling\Nwhat you feel is a spiritual obligation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.66,1:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people go through a period of vegetarianism, et cetera.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.12,1:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of one's intention to not harm living things.\NAnd you don't incur any karmic debt from that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.94,1:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NThe Rig Veda, you have to read the Rig Veda,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.18,1:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will understand what I'm saying.\NRig Veda.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.53,1:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Calories at 900.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.64,1:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing earns its own transcendence\Nby serving that which is below it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.15,1:14:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,By allowing myself to be eaten by humankind,\Nthe cattle earns its right to evolve
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.87,1:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually to humanness.\NBy my sacrifice to thee, O Lord of my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.27,1:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is higher,\Ndo I earn the karmic right to become higher?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.05,1:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary's 900.\NThe Rig Veda recontextualizes the whole question.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.01,1:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I once saw it.\NI saw a bird that was caught by a hawk,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.36,1:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw that the bird, I saw its spirit.\NIt supplicated itself to the hawk.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.76,1:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.86,1:14:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.98,1:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.06,1:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.14,1:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.26,1:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.32,1:14:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.36,1:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.40,1:14:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.44,1:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I give myself to thee, O Lord, is what it was actually saying.\NI actually saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.30,1:14:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the hawk again will surrender that which I am to thee, O Lord.\NAnd each one goes higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.21,1:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually witnessed it long before I read it in the Rig Veda.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.24,1:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I also get a blessing for my husband and I?\NWe're recently married.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.02,1:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing for what?\NHer husband and I were recently married.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.79,1:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.92,1:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have his promotion, too.\NThe Native American manner of holding, the sacredness of the spirit of the animal, is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.95,1:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,another way of acknowledging the divinity of the essence of life in all that lives,\Nand giving thanks to Almighty God for the life of the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.04,1:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So the American Indian, you know, blesses the sacrifice of the animal, and thereby, you know,\Nand thereby, affirms the divinity of all of life, you know, the sacredness of the great spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.45,1:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Native American acknowledges the great spirit as a source of life.\NSo, God bless the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.67,1:16:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NGod bless you in love, in love, and alignment in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.28,1:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NAnd in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.44,1:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.54,1:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
