Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.66,1:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.70,1:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.78,1:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.82,1:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.10,1:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.14,1:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.18,1:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
