Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.76,1:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.54,1:16:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.68,1:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.80,1:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.86,1:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.90,1:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.44,1:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going through a stack two weeks ago, and didn't get to sign the card, so I got\Nyou another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.68,1:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.\NHere's a dollar for the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.50,1:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.61,1:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The stack has got to do with two things, but one of them is for the many years.\Nvarious people connected to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.10,1:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a now deceased guru.\NConnected to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.40,1:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To a now deceased guru.\NTo what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.32,1:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A deceased guru.\NOr deceased.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.32,1:17:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceased.\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.10,1:17:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very large organization\Nand there are many people in there
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.38,1:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who on many levels\Nare very wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.41,1:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NAnd I know that at one point
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.65,1:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this guru calibrated fairly high\Nin the high 500s and then fell.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.07,1:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI don't get that it was about sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.61,1:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,power, or those other things.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.01,1:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be for opening up students\Nwithout properly preparing them?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.10,1:17:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be any defect.\NWhat do you mean the guru fell?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.55,1:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher fell?\NThe teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.51,1:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that I don't have.\NI know that you had calibrated him
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.07,1:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at around 570\Nand then he went down to the 100s.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.86,1:18:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather common, yeah.\NAnd I don't get that it was for the usual ones
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.14,1:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or money, power, sex.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.56,1:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't get that from...\NYou don't know what the reason is?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.98,1:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYou'd have to be more involved
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.84,1:18:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it'll become apparent.\NI don't want to be more involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.42,1:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The person will become more secular,\Nmore interested in money, fame, power, glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.74,1:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be any one of them.\NWould opening...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.24,1:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Energetically opening a huge amount,\Na mass of people
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.90,1:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without properly preparing them,\Nwould that also be one of...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.93,1:18:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be a spiritual trap?\NThat'd be a control issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.41,1:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a control issue.\NIt's kind of a research question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.37,1:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a research question,\Nbut what you're presenting as a possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.91,1:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is you're going to force people\Nto desire spiritual awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.55,1:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without their agreement, you know?\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.57,1:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm also thinking of myself\Nas a teacher and my responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.97,1:19:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to my students in terms of\Nis there a line?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.24,1:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there is no real line\Nfor any of this, is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.16,1:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, there is.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.94,1:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's definitely a line.\NSo where do I find that line?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.00,1:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?\NYou're mixing up a whole bunch of issues here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.96,1:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...\NYou're vague on your question,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.40,1:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's very difficult.\NYou can't control the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.60,1:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of your students,\Nand you've got to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.26,1:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to control that, right?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.28,1:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to force them\Nto become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.18,1:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.86,1:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like the Shaktipat,\Nwhich would be a forceful issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.06,1:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is\Nyou give them the information they need.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.78,1:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NAnd as much encouragement as you can,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.24,1:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but then the evolution is up to themselves,\Nyou see?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.46,1:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yes.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.52,1:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you teach them a certain technique\Nthat will help them
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.14,1:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve their spiritual goals, you know?\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.94,1:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so techniques are useful,\Nbut they're only a technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.22,1:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.80,1:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NYou know,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.30,1:20:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,like surrendering the,\Nresisting the experiencing of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.32,1:20:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,\Nit's only a technique, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.36,1:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.50,1:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.81,1:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hustle.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.89,1:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.\NThis morning was exceptional
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.79,1:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in its clarity\Nand expansion
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.25,1:20:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of our learning your work.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.56,1:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a group\Nthat meets twice a month in Phoenix,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.83,1:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and what we've been doing\Nis showing a DVD
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.37,1:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of a Sedona,\NSedona presentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.93,1:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NIt's on a weeknight evening,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.31,1:20:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so we only have like an hour and a half to two hours.\NSome are requesting that we pick a book
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.83,1:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and go through a paragraph at a time,\Nand others prefer that we watch a DVD
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.14,1:21:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a more like an overview.\NYou can do it both ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.13,1:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes if you meet twice a week,\None night you do a video,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.13,1:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next night you do a discussion,\Nor discuss a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.73,1:21:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.95,1:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, both ways are used,\Nyou know, like in AA,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.95,1:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,they will take a lesson for the day,\N12 steps,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.95,1:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll do a step or a tradition,\Nor because nowadays we have DVDs,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.68,1:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, they do a video.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.97,1:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.06,1:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.56,1:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.00,1:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I've been doing a lot of releasing,\Nand now it just feels like
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.00,1:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really feel any,\Nyou know,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.10,1:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,emotions coming up,\Nbut only the,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.10,1:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess,\Nthe physical sensations in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.10,1:22:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering,\Nis that normal,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.45,1:22:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or am I actually supposed to be feeling something\Nwhen I'm surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.45,1:22:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's normal.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.40,1:22:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any,\NI mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.40,1:22:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,additional advice that you can...\NAbout what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.40,1:22:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...collaborate?\NAdvice on what he should be doing,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.40,1:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,where to take it from...\NWhat he should be doing about what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.00,1:22:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, yeah,\Nwhere to take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.15,1:22:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know where to go from here.\NFrom where?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.56,1:22:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get where,\Nfrom where?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.56,1:22:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat it one more time.\NIf he's finding physical,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.80,1:22:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you know...\NI'm only feeling,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.84,1:22:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,like, physical sensations,\Nusually around,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.84,1:22:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess,\Nthe solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.87,1:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NOh, let go in to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.87,1:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting it.\NLet go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.28,1:22:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And go in to change it.\NLet it be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.28,1:23:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.56,1:23:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThe way you disappear a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.81,1:23:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is by letting go resisting it.\NI'm afraid that I'm actually,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.26,1:23:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like,\Nactively suppressing,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.26,1:23:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like,\Nnegative emotions or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.26,1:23:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid of what?\NSuppressing a negative emotion
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.26,1:23:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.26,1:23:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nif you're suppressing
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.26,1:23:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a negative emotion,\Nthe way to clear it
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.26,1:23:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is to let go resisting it.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.51,1:23:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to get rid of pain\Nis to let go resisting the pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.51,1:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've got to be right on it\Nas it arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.67,1:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it will disappear.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.18,1:23:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were telling earlier,\Nabout an hour ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.25,1:23:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,about when you make,\NI'm going to say
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.25,1:23:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the ultimate\Nlast step
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.25,1:24:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or something\Nwhen you go through
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.25,1:24:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the door.\NAnd I was,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.48,1:24:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have someone,\NI know someone
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.60,1:24:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that did that\Nand I was wondering,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.60,1:24:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the ultimate\Nwhen you go through
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.60,1:24:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that door and...\NThe door I'm talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.60,1:24:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is final.\NBut you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.60,1:24:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.05,1:24:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NEgo,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.05,1:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that which\Nwas presumed
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.40,1:24:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to be me\Ndisappeared
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.40,1:24:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a long time ago.\NSo,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.53,1:24:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,after you go...\NThe physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.53,1:24:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has its own\Nprotoplasm
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.53,1:24:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and,\Nthe protoplasm
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.53,1:24:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has its own\Nkarmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.53,1:24:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing\Nto do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.56,1:24:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Nmy question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.79,1:24:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,after you go\Nthrough that door,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.92,1:24:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what level\Nof calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.08,1:24:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are you at?\NI don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.08,1:24:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is\Nany calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.08,1:24:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's\Nnobody to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.08,1:24:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That state\Nof consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.08,1:24:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're\Nasking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.08,1:24:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.08,1:24:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The void\Nis at 850.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.08,1:24:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.08,1:24:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The void\Nis at 850.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.08,1:25:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you come\Ninto the,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.24,1:25:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess,\Nwhat you would call
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.24,1:25:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the 900s,\Nno?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.24,1:25:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NAnyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.24,1:25:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that's covered\Nin Transcending
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.24,1:25:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the Levels\Nof Consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.24,1:25:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and that book\Nthere will tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.24,1:25:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the final\Nchapters,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.24,1:25:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,yes.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.24,1:25:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a gift\Nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.24,1:25:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's,\Nin 1992,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.24,1:25:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Teresa\Naddressed
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.24,1:25:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the Scripps\Nclinical staff
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.24,1:25:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,after she recovered\Nfrom her
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.24,1:25:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,heart problem\Nand she just
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.24,1:25:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,talks for\N40 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.24,1:25:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's\Namazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.24,1:25:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How very nice\Nindeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.24,1:25:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NWe treasure
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.24,1:25:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,those things.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.64,1:25:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's back\Nin the news
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.50,1:25:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,currently,\Nhuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.24,1:25:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI wonder
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.58,1:26:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can\Nhelp me
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.58,1:26:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with my\Nchemical imbalance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.58,1:26:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With your\Nwhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.58,1:26:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chemical\Nimbalance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.58,1:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chemical\Nimbalance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.58,1:26:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a chemical\Nproblem.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.58,1:26:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nyou told me
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.58,1:26:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,not to use\Nthe word
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.58,1:26:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,depression\Nin the past
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.58,1:26:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm trying\Nto use
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.58,1:26:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the word\Ndepression.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.68,1:26:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,\Nokay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.68,1:26:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.68,1:26:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.68,1:26:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI said
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.68,1:26:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a\Nclinical
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.68,1:26:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,problem\Nof brain
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.68,1:26:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,chemistry.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.68,1:26:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NSo now
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.68,1:26:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what?\NSo I've
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.68,1:26:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,been having\Nthis feeling
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.68,1:26:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,toward myself\Nand I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.68,1:26:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NHerself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.06,1:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about\Nherself?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.17,1:26:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got\Nthings
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.17,1:26:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,involved.\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.17,1:26:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway,\NI can't stop
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.17,1:27:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the thoughts.\NAre you seeing
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.17,1:27:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a doctor like\Nadvice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.32,1:27:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,\Nyeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.99,1:27:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NTell him
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.99,1:27:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,about that.\NWhat spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.99,1:27:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,problem\Nyou got?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.99,1:27:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\NGood girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.99,1:27:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,\NI got
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.99,1:27:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,some\Nabout thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.63,1:27:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,negative thoughts\Nthat come
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.63,1:27:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,on their\Nown that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.63,1:27:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not,\Nyou know,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.63,1:27:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not\Nlooking for
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.63,1:27:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,them.\NThey're just
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.63,1:27:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,other than\Nprayer and
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.63,1:27:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation\Nand commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.63,1:27:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that takes\Ncare of
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.63,1:27:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual\Nand biochemistry
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.63,1:27:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,takes care\Nof the physical
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.85,1:27:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and between\Nthe two of
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.85,1:27:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,them,\Nyou're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.85,1:27:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,all you can\Ndo and
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.85,1:27:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore\Nyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.85,1:27:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that is true.\NLots of things
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.85,1:27:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are uncomfortable.\NJust being alive
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.85,1:27:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is uncomfortable.\NI know
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.85,1:27:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you're doing\Nbetter.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.84,1:28:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better\Nthan you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.68,1:28:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're much\Nbetter.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.68,1:28:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say\Nsome,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.72,1:28:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,some spiritual\Nservice
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.72,1:28:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere\Nthat you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.72,1:28:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,earn the karmic\Nmerit that
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.72,1:28:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,those kinds\Nof thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.72,1:28:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,be removed\Nfrom you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.72,1:28:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.04,1:28:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working\Non that already.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.04,1:28:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very\Nmuch.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.04,1:28:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That means a\Nlot to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.04,1:28:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because\Nyou're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.04,1:28:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're,\Nyou know,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.04,1:28:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you\Nto do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.04,1:28:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NDoing what
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.04,1:28:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you\Nto do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.07,1:28:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No,\Nyou're much
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.07,1:28:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,better.\NAnd I
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.07,1:28:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,think,\NI think some
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.07,1:28:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,service,\Nsome place
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.07,1:28:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in your life,\NI don't see
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.07,1:28:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,service yet.\NSome area
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.07,1:28:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of service.\NHumane
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.07,1:28:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,society.\NYeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.07,1:28:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,something.\NTake your
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.07,1:28:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,flowers to\NWell,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.07,1:28:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already\Nselling,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.07,1:29:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm selling\Nnewspapers for
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.07,1:29:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,real change,\Nwhich is,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.07,1:29:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,\Nfor homeless
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.07,1:29:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and people.\NOh,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.07,1:29:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very\Ngood,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.07,1:29:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah.\NAnd,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.07,1:29:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and people\Nwho,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.07,1:29:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,\Nare just
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.07,1:29:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,making it.\NAnd I'm one
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.07,1:29:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ones\Nthat is just
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.26,1:29:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,making it,\Nso I'm doing
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.26,1:29:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it for the,\Nyeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.80,1:29:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,doing,\Nshe's doing
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.80,1:29:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,up there as\Nwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.60,1:29:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From hopeless\Nto hopeful.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.43,1:29:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NHi,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.43,1:29:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.\NHawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.43,1:29:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a\Nquestion about
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.43,1:29:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,my personal\Nlife.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.43,1:29:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a\Nboyfriend that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.43,1:29:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect\Nis not
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.43,1:29:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,at the\Ncalibratable
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.43,1:29:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,level of\N200.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.43,1:29:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I\Nthink
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.43,1:29:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.\NAnd if
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.43,1:29:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose\Nto be
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.75,1:29:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,at the\Ncalibratable
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.75,1:29:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,level,\Nis it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.75,1:29:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,likely that\Nhe will
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.75,1:30:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,raise his\Ncalibratable
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.10,1:30:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,level up\Nor that I
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.10,1:30:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,might,\Nmy level
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.54,1:30:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,might come\Ndown?
